Now,
 $$
\begin{align}
\mathbb{R}^3
&=
\operatorname{Span}\left(\begin{pmatrix}-1\\2\\0\end{pmatrix},
\begin{pmatrix}0\\0\\1\end{pmatrix},
\begin{pmatrix}1\\-2\\0\end{pmatrix}\right)\\
\operatorname{Proj}_\mathbf{w}
\begin{pmatrix}0\\1\\4\end{pmatrix}
&=
\mathbf{w},
\end{align}
$$
and since
$$
\operatorname{proj}_\mathbf{u}\mathbf{v}
=
\frac{\langle\mathbf{v},\mathbf{u}\rangle}{\|\mathbf{u}\|^2}\,\mathbf{u}
$$
allows us to calculate the desired result.
$ \Box$
<formula>
\begin{align}
\operatorname{proj}_\mathbf{w}
\begin{pmatrix}3\\3\\-2\end{pmatrix}
&=
\frac{\langle\begin{pmatrix}3\\3\\-2\end{pmatrix},
\begin{pmatrix}1\\-1/2\\1/2\end{pmatrix}\rangle}{
\big\|\begin{pmatrix}1\\-1/2\\1/2\end{pmatrix}\big\|^2}
\begin{pmatrix}1\\-1/2\\1/2\end{pmatrix}\\
&=
\frac{3-3-1}{2}
\begin{pmatrix}1\\-1/2\\1/2\end{pmatrix}\\
&=
\frac{-1}{2}
\begin{pmatrix}1\\-1/2\\1/2\end{pmatrix}\\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}-1/2\\1/4\\-1/4\end{pmatrix}
\end{align}
</formula>

